{"TopicId":142899,"ForumId":46,"TopicTitle":"The Grand \u0026quot;Imgur albums/links are broken\u0026quot; thread.","CreatedByName":"Bloojay","CreatedById":162865,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-01T11:54:46Z","PageNum":6,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-15T18:30:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/131481-stickman939/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022131481\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/131481-stickman939/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@stickman939\u003C/a\u003E, so the thread with which yours has been merged. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MatterBeam","CreatedById":133334,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-27T14:27:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere \u0027i\u0027 icon on the top left of the editing bar is gone. The [imgur] tags do not work.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHas the option to ember imgur albums been removed?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Tex_NL","CreatedById":58254,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-27T14:39:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s been broken for at least half a year. Probably longer, perhaps even a year.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"James Kerman","CreatedById":160462,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-27T15:12:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can embed Imgur using using the HTML link.\u00A0 Just drop it in and the forum will recognise it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Frank_G","CreatedById":100000,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-27T15:24:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222866016\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022152658\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221480259567\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022160462\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022James Kerman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n11 minutes ago, James Kerman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can embed Imgur using using the HTML link.\u00A0 Just drop it in and the forum will recognise it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDoes this include albums?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"James Kerman","CreatedById":160462,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-27T15:27:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo albums are definitely broken.\u00A0 Most members are posting an example image and linking to the albums .\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MatterBeam","CreatedById":133334,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-27T16:02:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222866026\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022152658\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221480260427\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022160462\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022James Kerman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n35 minutes ago, James Kerman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo albums are definitely broken.\u00A0 Most members are posting an example image and linking to the albums .\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks, I\u0027ll do this.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"septemberWaves","CreatedById":160814,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-27T16:22:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAn alternative is to post an example image in the main post, and then put the rest of the images with descriptions in a spoiler beneath. This is what I\u0027ve been doing lately, and it\u0027s quite effective - especially since more often than not, imgur now randomly re-orders the images in an album after a while.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Red Iron Crown","CreatedById":12858,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-27T17:43:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/133334-matterbeam/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022133334\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/133334-matterbeam/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@MatterBeam\u003C/a\u003E Merged your thread into the big thread about imgur albums embeds being broken.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"swjr-swis","CreatedById":152460,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-27T18:40:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222841948\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022142899\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221478520798\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002212858\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Red Iron Crown\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 11/7/2016 at 1:13 PM, Red Iron Crown said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe\u0027re still waiting on the forum software update at this point.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRIC, any update on this status?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Red Iron Crown","CreatedById":12858,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-27T20:08:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222866242\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022142899\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221480272027\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022152460\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022swjr-swis\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, swjr-swis said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents ipsClearfix\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRIC, any update on this status?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nStill waiting on the forum software update before resuming testing. There were some technical issues with applying the update, hopefully it will be done Soon(tm).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mad Rocket Scientist","CreatedById":139256,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-23T20:50:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222866016\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022142899\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221480259567\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022160462\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022James Kerman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 11/27/2016 at 7:12 AM, James Kerman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can embed Imgur using using the HTML link.\u00A0 Just drop it in and the forum will recognise it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis doesn\u0027t work for me:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u0026lt;blockquote class=\u0022img